{
  "stem": "9245.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we knew we didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One night, we stayed in his barn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And at that time, since Jews started-- by the way, the shooting was going on from the trains, because Jews were jumping from the trains.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the Germans were shooting them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some were lucky to not to caught a bullet, and some were killed right on the spot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "By the same token, there were an awful lot-- not an awful lot-- quite a few gentiles that were roaming, already, the forests, for the purpose of robbing Jews.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They knew that Jews escaped from the ghetto, and they had with  them some jewelery or some money.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That night, as we were staying in that barn, and this-- this gentile fellow came in with a couple-- he had two girls with him-- with him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, they were Jewish girls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But he-- his purpose was rob Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The girls didn't mean much to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he introduced himself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] His name was Hodunko, H-O-D-U-N-K-O.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He was a known robber, a known fugitive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he said to my father, oh, nice seeing you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I'll be seeing you around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That was a-- a-- a-- a hint that we cannot-- we could not stay in this place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The-- the-- that Vasill came-- came over the next morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He said, he's a dangerous man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You better don't face him anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he put us up about a couple kilometers from the house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father took off his coat, and he gave it to him and a pair of boots.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, that's all I can give you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't have anything else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you will try to feed us as much as you can.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So every-- we didn't-- we were sitting just in the bushes.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
